  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Empower with art 800 citizens in Colombia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Citizens from marginalized neighborhoods in Bogota are being stigmatized and are left behind by society and the government. Without sufficient voice and visibility, they constantly suffer abuses and see their quality of life diminished. We want to empower them by co-creating public space art that highlights their identity, dreams and citizen engagement, to turn their places from being perceived as criminal hotspots into cultural hubs.</narrative>
  </description>
